doc_summary_long: Ten people, including two who were found Monday, have had fatal incidents inside the Eagle's Nest cave dive area in Western Florida since 1981. 'Eagle's Nest is an alluring cave and many divers aspire to dive there someday,' she said. 'Even with that experience things can go wrong, but as cave divers we all know the risks before we go.'
